      "content": "it's not a \"chapter\" though. a chapter implies there's a book that keeps going. but there's no book. i've reached the end of the line. everything i've contributed is garbage, and the person who contributed it shouldn't even be taking up space in the world. it feels like the most dignified, most logical thing would be to just let the silence take over. to just finally admit that the performance is over and be done with it. why should i keep dragging this out?",
